  <brief_title>Evaluate Anti-adhesive Effect and Safety of a Mixed Solid of Poloxamer, Gelatin and Chitosan(Mediclore®)</brief_title>
  <acronym>antiadhesion</acronym>
  <official_title>Evaluate Anti-adhesive Effect and Safety of a Mixed Solid of Poloxamer, Gelatin and Chitosan(Mediclore®) for Intraperitoneal Adhesion in Patient With Gynecological Surgery, a Multicenter Single-blinded, Randomized Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
