  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy and safety of Mediclore®, as an
      antiadhesive barrier, which is made of Poloxamer, Gelatin and Chitosan.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
